			<div class="entry">

				<p>Random amusement from SNL last week:</p>
<p><object width="512" height="288"><param name="movie" value="http://www.hulu.com/embed/DugTFCl5E_pUZYXFlvWx3A"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><embed src="http://www.hulu.com/embed/DugTFCl5E_pUZYXFlvWx3A" type="application/x-shockwave-flash"  width="512" height="288" allowFullScreen="true"></embed></object></p>

